Key Match Events: Saud Shakeel scored 68 runs for Pakistan
Vikramjit Singh scored 52 runs for Netherlands
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at Rajiv Gandhi International Stadium, Uppal, Hyderabad
Pakistan scored 286 runs in 49 overs, while Netherlands managed 205 runs in 41 overs
Others: The match was a day-night 50-over match
The match was part of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023-24
Saud Shakeel was named Player of the Match
